description:
A young woman who snatched the lips of an Ochibito and turned her partner into a Kamibito.
It was the boy who actually started it, but she was still executed by the laws of the Kamibito.
Whatever reason there might have been, to turn an Ochibito into a Kamibito is a serious crime and needs to be punished according to the law.
name: Itsukushima Kanako
